{"tid":1300465,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[鏗鏘集：這年初夏]睇左3分鐘就忍唔住流淚","createTime":"2019-07-09T11:21:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T15:15:03.000Z","uid":59618,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"11be95902478a65a7492d52ad0fd6fa40b52c390","tid":1300465,"uid":59618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:21:00.000Z","msg":"自問自己本身唔係眼淺既男人,但呢個月黎,每次睇抗爭既片,都好易流眼淚. 我唔知我喊係因為感動,係因為政權,定因為人性既醜陋.<br />\n<br />\n發自內心,好感激你地每一個肯行出黎既人..每次抗爭我都係獨行俠,因為我身邊所有朋友都係港豬.<br />\n但每次出黎我唔覺得孤單,因為我知道你地每一個人都係向住同一個目標進發. 令我徹底係呢一個月改變我對00後甚至係香港人既睇法.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aeMIHmpRyAg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DaeMIHmpRyAg&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7KZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=c3ea566e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aeMIHmpRyAg</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n條片我忍左好耐, 到最後個女仔講呢幾句話,我真係忍唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">縱然這段時間會感到灰心,失望,無力.但切記絕不可感到絕望. 雖然不知黑暗會持續多久,但請相信,光明最終會戰勝黑暗</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最後,有兩首歌,我每次聽都會燃起我團火<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g9RjV-zeZz0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dg9RjV-zeZz0&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7KZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=f29bdd49\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=g9RjV-zeZz0</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ukhKS3aaHxE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DukhKS3aaHxE&d=xVNj5QJXHW0KkW%2Bw8ZKC7KZPNspveiVXvfzVSLwjqls%3D&h=554f5fe7\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ukhKS3aaHxE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n政府越黎越多醜聞爆出,大家一齊努力,保護屬於我地既城市<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a96ad7bc222e05ad9b23f93c52168849a687a6d1","tid":1300465,"uid":270346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-09T11:23:5